Class DefaultAlternativePaymentOrderStatusService

  • java.lang.Object
    • isv.sap.payment.service.alternativepayment.DefaultAlternativePaymentOrderStatusService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AlternativePaymentOrderStatusService

    public class DefaultAlternativePaymentOrderStatusService
extends java.lang.Object
implements AlternativePaymentOrderStatusService
    Encapsulates the default implementation of AlternativePaymentOrderStatusService interface.

    Defines default implementation logic for alternative payment status like: check, count and update.
